This is Task 3 of 10. We're adding TISInputSource API support for switching keyboard layouts (Korean/English/etc). The CJKV double-switch workaround is critical — TISSelectInputSource has a known macOS bug where switching TO CJKV input sources fails. The workaround first switches to ABC/US, waits, then switches to the target.

