## F003: 키 이름→keycode 매핑 테이블

파일: `src/utils.ts`

기존 `keycodeSchema`를 찾아주세요 (`Grep`으로 검색). 그 근처에 매핑 테이블을 추가합니다.

```typescript
export const KEY_NAME_MAP: Record<string, number> = {
  // Modifiers
  command: 55, cmd: 55, leftcommand: 55,
  rightcommand: 54, rcmd: 54,
  shift: 56, leftshift: 56,
  rightshift: 60, rshift: 60,
  option: 58, alt: 58, leftoption: 58,
  rightoption: 61, ralt: 61, roption: 61,
  control: 59, ctrl: 59, leftcontrol: 59,
  rightcontrol: 62, rctrl: 62,
  capslock: 57, fn: 63,
  // Special
  return: 36, enter: 36,
  tab: 48, space: 49,
  delete: 51, backspace: 51,
  forwarddelete: 117,
  escape: 53, esc: 53,
  // Arrow keys
  up: 126, down: 125, left: 123, right: 124,
  // Navigation
  home: 115, end: 119, pageup: 116, pagedown: 121,
  // Letters (QWERTY)
  a: 0, s: 1, d: 2, f: 3, h: 4, g: 5, z: 6, x: 7, c: 8, v: 9,
  b: 11, q: 12, w: 13, e: 14, r: 15, y: 16, t: 17, o: 31, u: 32,
  i: 34, p: 35, l: 37, j: 38, k: 40, n: 45, m: 46,
  // Numbers
  "0": 29, "1": 18, "2": 19, "3": 20, "4": 21, "5": 23, "6": 22, "7": 26, "8": 28, "9": 25,
  // Function keys
  f1: 122, f2: 120, f3: 99, f4: 118, f5: 96, f6: 97,
  f7: 98, f8: 100, f9: 101, f10: 109, f11: 103, f12: 111,
  // Punctuation
  minus: 27, equal: 24, leftbracket: 33, rightbracket: 30,
  semicolon: 41, quote: 39, comma: 43, period: 47, slash: 44, backslash: 42,
  grave: 50, // backtick
};

export function resolveKeycode(value: number | string): number {
  if (typeof value === "number") return value;
  const lower = value.toLowerCase().replace(/[\s_-]/g, "");
  const code = KEY_NAME_MAP[lower];
  if (code === undefined) {
    throw new Error(`Unknown key name: '${value}'. Use a numeric keycode (0-255) or a known name.`);
  }
  return code;
}
```

## F004: Zod 스키마 확장

파일: `src/utils.ts` (keycodeSchema) + `src/tools/input.ts` (빌드 함수)

1. `keycodeSchema`를 변경:
```typescript
// Before:
export const keycodeSchema = z.number().int().min(0).max(255);
// After:
export const keycodeSchema = z.union([
  z.number().int().min(0).max(255),
  z.string().min(1),
]).describe("HID keycode (0-255) or key name (e.g. 'command', 'shift', 'a', 'f1')");
```

2. `src/tools/input.ts`의 buildKeyArgs, buildKeySequenceArgs, buildKeyComboArgs에서 keycode를 resolve:

```typescript
// buildKeyArgs:
const args = ["key", String(resolveKeycode(params.keycode))];

// buildKeySequenceArgs:
const keycodes = Array.isArray(params.keycodes)
  ? params.keycodes.map(k => resolveKeycode(k)).join(",")
  : params.keycodes;  // 문자열은 그대로 (쉼표 구분 숫자)

// buildKeyComboArgs:
return [
  "key-combo",
  "--modifiers",
  params.modifiers.map(m => resolveKeycode(m)).join(","),
  "--key",
  String(resolveKeycode(params.key)),
  ...target,
];
```

3. `resolveKeycode`를 `src/utils.ts`에서 import.

4. 타입 업데이트 — `KeyParams`, `KeySequenceParams`, `KeyComboParams`에서 keycode 타입을 `number | string`으로.

